                    <span>I have been searching for a resource to assist me in learning assembly language for a long time.  I purchased a couple books but they only focus on linux in a mininmal way.  Linux is the primary focus of this book.  I have found this book the best assembly book for a linux user to learn assembly.</span>
                  
